img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7161ecf58ab4b7daa643e03c11e6196cd5e0d2ce","tid":23280,"uid":33970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:03:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌 上次我用膠袋捉左隻大強<br />\n係個膠袋口倒左50ml 75度既酒精去浸佢<br />\n隻強浸住酒精掙扎左成分幾鐘先死<br />\n仲要係咁向上爬撞個膠袋結<br />\n我隻手渣住個膠袋結係咁feel到佢個頭撞上黎<br />\n有d野吉下吉下咁幾驚個膠袋穿左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要就打死佢啦 令佢死得咁痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗住佢一浸就死架嘛 點知咁耐都唔死之餘<br />\n仲猛咁掙紮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打死佢又成地汁咁核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923ad01651347bd5d269a67ca3d33a6f41a8ccfa","tid":23280,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:05:02.000Z","msg":"酒精邊殺得死<br />\n我教你 噴天拿水 好撚快死"},{"pid":"894fc33d2ffe6fb15b87fe4d915a86010831f73b","tid":23280,"uid":18814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:05:41.000Z","msg":"小強用油層去阻止水份進入身體<br />\n酒精破壞酒層 令大量液體進入小強體內<br />\n小強體內爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3373715e38da5dc85840762f8cc42d7f7daad2","tid":23280,"uid":49142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:07:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小強用油層去阻止水份進入身體<br />\n酒精破壞酒層 令大量液體進入小強體內<br />\n小強體內爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce65d1d33746c7897a7042619aeb95bcec95268d","tid":23280,"uid":10377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:09:54.000Z","msg":"用detergent仲快溶左佢層油"},{"pid":"23d148a79ac17dfc452ec742a19d2d8164edc57c","tid":23280,"uid":40460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"